いくぜ！！ 譲れない夢がある GO!
Let's go!! There is a dream we can't yield!

168
00:08:54,148 --> 00:08:57,648
いくぜ！！ 必ずゲットだぜ
Let's go!! We will definitely catch 'em all!

169
00:08:58,148 --> 00:09:02,148
いこうぜ！！ 手を伸ばして
Let's go!! Reach out your hand...

