204
00:12:47,023 --> 00:12:49,723
楽に 向こうの岸までつくけど
I can easily reach the other side

205
00:12:49,723 --> 00:12:51,123
何回やっても
But no matter how many times I try

206
00:12:51,123 --> 00:12:52,523
何回やっても
No matter how many times I try

207
