何回やっても 何回やっても
No matter how many times I try, no matter how many times I try,

208
00:15:02,511 --> 00:15:04,611
エアーマンが倒せないよ
I can't defeat Airman.

209
00:15:04,611 --> 00:15:07,711
あの竜巻何回やっても避けれない
I can't avoid that tornado no matter how many times I try.

210
00:15:07,711 --> 00:15:10,811
うしろに回って撃ち続けても
Even if I go behind him and keep shooting,

211
00:15:10,811 --> 00:15:13,111
