I'll eventually get blown away by the wind.

212
00:15:13,111 --> 00:15:15,711
タイム連打も試してみたけど
I tried rapid-firing the pause button too,

213
00:15:15,711 --> 00:15:18,411
竜巻相手じゃ意味が無い
But it's meaningless against the tornado!

214
00:15:18,411 --> 00:15:20,511
だから次は絶対勝つために
So, to make sure I win next time,

215
00:15:20,511 --> 00:15:23,411
僕はE缶だけは最後までとっておく
I'll save my E-tank until the very end.

216
00:15:23,411 --> 00:15:26,911
倒せないよ
I can't defeat him...

217
00:16:30,411 --> 00:16:35,411
ロボのテーマ
[On-Screen: Robo's Theme]

218
00:17:29,411 --> 00:17:34,411
カエルのテーマ
[On-Screen: Frog's Theme]

219
00:19:21,411 --> 00:19:26,411
Melodies Of Life
[On-Screen: Melodies Of Life]

220
00:19:34,911 --> 00:19:39,911
あてもなく 彷徨っていた
I wandered aimlessly,

221
