手がかりもなく探し続けた
Searching endlessly without any clues.

222
00:19:45,211 --> 00:19:50,011
あなたがくれた思い出を
Turning the memories you gave me...

223
00:19:50,011 --> 00:20:04,911
心を癒す歌にして
...into a song that heals my heart.

224
00:20:06,752 --> 00:20:13,952
約束もすることもなく
Without making promises,

225
