交わす言葉も決めたりもせず
Without even deciding on words to say,

226
00:20:21,752 --> 00:20:27,952
抱きしめ、そして確かめた
We held each other close, and made certain

227
00:20:27,952 --> 00:20:34,452
日々は二度と帰らぬ
That those days will never return.

228
00:20:36,952 --> 00:20:48,952
記憶の中の手を振るあなたは
You, waving your hand in my memories...

229
00:20:49,452 --> 00:20:58,952
わたしの名を呼ぶことができるの？
Are you able to call out my name?

230
00:21:03,952 --> 00:21:10,452
あふれるその涙を
Turn those overflowing tears...

231
00:21:10,452 --> 00:21:17,952
輝く夢に変えて
...into a shining dream.

232
00:21:18,452 --> 00:21:24,452
いのちはつづく
Life goes on,

233
00:21:24,952 --> 00:21:27,952
夜を越え
Crossing over the night,

234
00:21:28,452 --> 00:21:35,952
疑うことのない明日へとつづく
Continuing on toward an indubitable tomorrow.

235
00:22:23,452 --> 00:22:29,952
飛ぶ鳥の向こうの空へ
To the sky beyond the flying birds,

236
00:22:29,952 --> 00:22:36,952
いくつの記憶預けただろう
How many memories have we entrusted?

237
00:22:37,452 --> 00:22:43,952
儚い希望も夢も
Fleeting hopes and dreams alike,

238
00:22:44,452 --> 00:22:50,952
届かぬ場所に忘れて
Forgotten in an unreachable place.

239
00:22:53,452 --> 00:23:05,452
めぐり逢うのは偶然と言えるの？
Can we say our meeting was just a coincidence?

240
00:23:05,952 --> 00:23:18,952
別れる時が必ず来るのに
Even though the time to part will surely come...

241
00:23:19,952 --> 00:23:26,952
消えゆく運命でも
Even if it is a fleeting destiny,

242
00:23:26,952 --> 00:23:33,952
君が生きている限り
As long as you are alive...

243
00:23:33,952 --> 00:23:40,952
いのちはつづく
Life goes on,

244
00:23:40,952 --> 00:23:44,452
永遠に
Eternally,

245
00:23:44,452 --> 00:23:52,952
その力の限りどこまでも
To wherever, as long as that strength lasts.

246
00:23:55,952 --> 00:24:01,952
わたしが死のうとも
Even if I should die,

247
00:24:02,452 --> 00:24:08,952
君が生きている限り
As long as you are alive...

248
00:24:09,452 --> 00:24:16,452
いのちはつづく
Life goes on,

249
00:24:16,452 --> 00:24:19,952
永遠に
Eternally,

250
00:24:20,452 --> 00:24:24,452
その力の限り
As long as that strength lasts,

251
00:24:24,452 --> 00:24:36,452
