It will continue forever.

252
00:25:10,660 --> 00:25:15,860
きみの瞳に映る
What color am I...

253
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:22,160
わたしは何色ですか
...in your eyes?

254
00:25:22,560 --> 00:25:29,260
赤深き望むなら
If you wish for a deep red,

255
00:25:29,260 --> 00:25:37,560
渡そう 陽の光を
I will give you the sunlight.

256
00:25:41,160 --> 00:26:00,560
Ah...

257
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:06,660
悲しみが溢れ
Overflowing with sadness,

258
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:12,760
瞼閉じました
I closed my eyelids.

259
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:19,160
こぼれた滴は
The spilled teardrops

260
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:25,060
心に沁みゆく
seep into my heart.

261
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:30,960
行き渡る波は
The spreading waves

262
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:36,460
弱く交えます
are weakly mingled.

263
00:26:37,260 --> 00:26:42,860
とどけしゆりかご
Delivered cradle,

264
00:26:42,860 --> 00:26:48,860
眠りをさそう
inviting sleep.

265
00:26:49,660 --> 00:26:55,160
夢になつかし
Searching for nostalgic images

266
00:26:55,160 --> 00:27:00,660
面影をさがす
in my dreams.

267
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:06,660
手を伸ばし強く
Stretching out my hand, strongly

268
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:13,860
抱きしめたくなる
I want to hold you tight...

269
00:27:15,260 --> 00:27:20,860
きみの瞳に映る
What color am I...

270
00:27:20,860 --> 00:27:27,260
わたしは何色ですか
...in your eyes?

271
00:27:28,060 --> 00:27:33,960
藍深き望むなら
If you wish for a deep indigo,

272
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:44,060
渡そう高き空を
I will give you the high sky.

273
00:27:54,060 --> 00:28:00,260
不安定な神様 繰り返す出会いと別れ
An unstable god, repeating meetings and partings.

274
00:28:00,260 --> 00:28:08,560
また会える その日まで 解きかける旅人
Until the day we meet again, a traveler solving riddles.

275
00:28:18,560 --> 00:28:24,260
あなたが泣いている 流る涙の雨
You are crying, a rain of flowing tears.

276
00:28:24,260 --> 00:28:30,460
泣くなとは言わない 心悲しくて
I won't tell you not to cry, with a sad heart.

277
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:36,460
生きて行けるもの 何かを背負いながら
Living on, while carrying something,

278
00:28:36,460 --> 00:28:42,760
見えない鎖に繋がれている
we are bound by invisible chains.

279
00:28:42,860 --> 00:28:48,860
どれほど救われただろう あどけない笑顔に
How much I must have been saved by that innocent smile.

280
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:55,560
失くしたくはない
I don't want to lose it.

281
